LucidChart,is,diagram,and,chart,making,platform,Users,can,create,wireframes,charts,UML,more,and,share,them,easily,through,an,array,of,integration,options,The,interface,allows,users,to,drag,and,drop,the,pieces,of,their,diagrams,For,this,users,have,a,large,selections,and,shapes,and,texts,at,their,disposal,The,diagrams,can,be,published,as,PDFs,or,shared,through,various,web,platforms,such,as,Google,Drive,and,Apps,The,LucidChart,API,exposes,the,document,management,functionality,It,is,a,RESTful,API,that,returns,XML,encoded,data